FBIS4-278 "drafr067_c_94011" FBIS-AFR-94-067 Daily Report 6 Apr 1994 REPUBLIC OF SOUTH AFRICA IFP Military Instructor Reports 5,000 Trained Zulus IFP Military Instructor Reports 5,000 Trained Zulus MB0604185594 Johannesburg SAPA in English 1805 GMT 6 Apr 94 MB0604185594 Johannesburg SAPA English BFN [Text] Durban April 6 SAPA -- An Inkatha Freedom Party [IFP] self protection unit instructor, Mr Philip Powell, says there are 5,000 trained Zulus and that more will be trained despite the emergency regulations, SABC [South African Broadcasting Corporation] radio news reports. Mr Powell told the London DAILY MAIL on Wednesday [6 April] that if the ANC forced the government to invade kwaZulu, the area would be transformed into a powerful symbol and rallying point for the Zulus.
